Observability Platform Instrumentation Strategy
How I'd Think About This End-to-End
Before writing a single line of Alloy config, I'd want to establish the mental model first: you're instrumenting platform infrastructure — not a product team's microservice. The failure modes, blast radius, and consumer impact patterns are fundamentally different. A Nexus outage doesn't just break one team, it breaks every pipeline across the org. GitLab going down stops all development. That shapes everything from SLI choice to alerting thresholds.
Let me walk through how I'd approach this systematically.
